              <li> <a href="../Industrial-applications/index.html" title="Industry"
                  class="nav_size">Industry</a>
                <div class="sub_bx" style="display:none;">
                  <dl id="lk_3" class="transform">
                    <dt>
                      <h1>Industry</h1>
                      <p>Focus on intergrated solution for beverage and liquid
                        food, such as mineral water, Juice, carbonated beverage,
                        energy drinks, wine, beer, edible oil, dairy and dauily
                        care products, etc.</p>
                    </dt>
                    <dd> <a href="../Industrial-applications/can-filling-solution/index.html"
                        class="list">
                        <div class="img"><img src="../uploadfile/2023/0330/20230330120138999.jpg"
                            alt="CAN FILLING LINE SOLUTION"></div>
                        <h3>CAN FILLING LINE SOLUTION</h3>
                        <p>Provide solutions for various energy drinks, juice
                          drinks, carbonated beverages, milk, tea, alcohol, and
                          other cans filling</p>
                      </a> <a href="../Industrial-applications/glass-bottle-wine-filling-line-solution/index.html"
                        class="list">
                        <div class="img"><img src="../uploadfile/2023/0330/20230330120659203.jpg"
                            alt="GLASS BOTTLE FILLING LINE SOLUTION"></div>
                        <h3>GLASS BOTTLE FILLING LINE SOLUTION</h3>
                        <p>Glass bottle filling line working system is important
                          to know. Bottles driven by variable pitch screw are
                          transferred to rinsing part through bottle-inlet star
                          wheel. </p>
                      </a> <a href="../Industrial-applications/Juice-filling-line-solution/index.html"
                        class="list">
                        <div class="img"><img src="../uploadfile/2023/0203/20230203010938189.jpg"
                            alt="JUICE PRODUCTION LINE SOLUTION "></div>
                        <h3>JUICE PRODUCTION LINE SOLUTION </h3>
                        <p>KIWL Machine filling machines will provide different
                          solutions for different products. Every one of your
                          products will have its optional solution.</p>
                      </a> <a href="../Industrial-applications/csd-filling-line-solution/index.html"
                        class="list">
                        <div class="img"><img src="../uploadfile/2023/0203/20230203011156614.jpg"
                            alt="CARBONATED SOFT DRINK PRODUCTION LINE SOLUTION "></div>
                        <h3>CARBONATED SOFT DRINK PRODUCTION LINE SOLUTION </h3>
                        <p>This Carbonated Soft Drink production line is mainly
                          included beverage mixing system, like sugar melting
                          boiler, double filter, syrup pump,syrup cooling tank,
                          mixing tank, storage tank, etc, also included
                          carbonated drink filling machine, carbonation mixe</p>
                      </a> <a href="../Industrial-applications/water-filling-line-solution/index.html"
                        class="list">
                        <div class="img"><img src="../uploadfile/2023/0330/20230330121000444.jpg"
                            alt="WATER FILLING PRODUCTION LINE SOLUTION"></div>
                        <h3>WATER FILLING PRODUCTION LINE SOLUTION</h3>
                        <p>KIWL Machine, the expert in liquid product filling,
                          will always provide you with the best solution for
                          your products.</p>
                      </a> <a href="../Industrial-applications/5-gallon-filling-line-solution/index.html"
                        class="list">
                        <div class="img"><img src="../uploadfile/2023/0330/20230330121040657.jpg"
                            alt="5 GALLON FILLING LINE SOLUTION"></div>
                        <h3>5 GALLON FILLING LINE SOLUTION</h3>
                        <p>This line is mainly used for filling pure water or
                          mineral water of 3 &amp; 5 gallon bottle.</p>
                      </a> <a href="../Industrial-applications/auec-jam-production-line-souution/index.html"
                        class="list">
                        <div class="img"><img src="../uploadfile/2023/0203/20230203014905642.jpg"
                            alt="SAUCE JAM PRODUCTION LINE SOLUTION"></div>
                        <h3>SAUCE JAM PRODUCTION LINE SOLUTION</h3>
                      </a>
                      <p><a href="../Industrial-applications/auec-jam-production-line-souution/index.html"
                          class="list">We use a wide variety of filling valve
                          （Gravity、negative pressure、isobaric、piston type
                          etc.�?/p&gt; </a> <a href="../Industrial-applications/oil-filling-solution/index.html"
                          class="list"> </a></p>
                      <div class="img"><a href="../Industrial-applications/oil-filling-solution/index.html"
                          class="list"><img src="../uploadfile/2023/0330/20230330121133205.jpg"
                            alt="Oil PRODUCTION LINE SOLUTION"></a></div>
                      <a href="../Industrial-applications/oil-filling-solution/index.html"
                        class="list">
                        <h3>Oil PRODUCTION LINE SOLUTION</h3>
                        <p>Oil products include edible oil and industrial oil,
                          like peanut oil, palm oil, blended oil, and
                          lubricating oil etc.</p>
                      </a> </dd>
                  </dl>
